er, the hide also makes it insensitive."},{"version":"silver","text":"Its brain devel\u00ad oped when it began walking on hind legs. Its thick hide protects it even in magma."},{"version":"crystal","text":"By lightly spin\u00ad ning its drill- like horn, it can easily shatter even a diamond in the rough."},{"version":"ruby","text":"RHYDON\u2019s horn can crush even uncut diamonds. One sweeping blow of its tail can topple a building. This POK\u00e9MON\u2019s hide is extremely tough. Even direct cannon hits don\u2019t leave a scratch."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"RHYDON has a horn that serves as a drill. It is used for destroying rocks and boulders. This POK\u00e9MON occasionally rams into streams of magma, but the armor-like hide prevents it from feeling the heat."},{"version":"emerald","text":"Its horn, which rotates like a drill, destroys tall buildings with one strike. It stands on its hind legs, and its brain is well developed."},{"version":"firered","text":"It begins walking on its hind legs after evolution. It can punch holes through boulders with its horn."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"Protected by an armor-like hide, it is capable of living in molten lava of 3,600 degrees Fahrenheit."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Its brain developed after it stood up on its hind legs. Its drill horn bores tunnels through solid rock."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Its brain developed after it stood up on its hind legs. Its drill horn bores tunnels through solid rock."},{"version":"platinum","text":"Standing on its hind legs freed its forelegs and made it smarter. It is very forgetful, however."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"Its rugged hide protects it from even the heat of lava. However, the hide also makes it insensitive."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Its brain developed when it began walking on hind legs. Its thick hide protects it even in magma."},{"version":"black","text":"Standing on its hind legs freed its forelegs and made it smarter. It is very forgetful, however."},{"version":"white","text":"Standing on its hind legs freed its forelegs and made it smarter. It is very forgetful, however."},{"version":"black-2","text":"Standing on its hind legs freed its forelegs and made it smarter. It is very forgetful, however."},{"version":"white-2","text":"Standing on its hind legs freed its forelegs and made it smarter. It is very forgetful, however."},{"version":"x","text":"Protected by an armor-like hide, it is capable of living in molten lava of 3,600 degrees Fahrenheit."},{"version":"y","text":"It begins walking on its hind legs after evolution. It can punch holes through boulders with its horn."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Rhydon\u2019s horn can crush even uncut diamonds. One sweeping blow of its tail can topple a building. This Pok\u00e9mon\u2019s hide is extremely tough. Even direct cannon hits don\u2019t leave a scratch."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Rhydon has a horn that serves as a drill. It is used for destroying rocks and boulders. This Pok\u00e9mon occasionally rams into streams of magma, but the armor-like hide prevents it from feeling the heat."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Its brain developed when it began walking on its hind legs. Its armor-like hide even repels molten lava."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Its brain developed when it began walking on its hind legs. Its armor-like hide even repels molten lava."},{"version":"sword","text":"It begins walking on its hind legs after evolution. It can punch holes through boulders with its horn."},{"version":"shield","text":"Protected by an armor-like hide, it is capable of living in molten lava of 3,600 degrees Fahrenheit."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Rapidly rotates its horn to bore through bedrock. It swaggers around volcanic regions, protected from the lava's heat by its tough, armorlike hide."}],"evo":{"name":"rhyhorn","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,